objects.name: areas
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE areas (id TEXT, defaultname TEXT)

objects.name: continents
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE continents (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,                -- M49, ej. '150'
    defaultname TEXT NOT NULL
)

objects.name: countries
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE countries (id TEXT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL, alpha2may TEXT, alpha3may TEXT, numeric TEXT, defaultname TEXT)
rows: Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha

objects.name: country_groups
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE country_groups (
    id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    group_id TEXT NOT NULL,
    country_id TEXT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (group_id) REFERENCES groups(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (country_id) REFERENCES countries(id)
)

objects.name: dependencies
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE dependencies (parent_id TEXT NOT NULL, dependent_id TEXT NOT NULL, id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT)

objects.name: groups
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE groups (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    defaultname TEXT NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
)

objects.name: languages
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE languages (id TEXT PRIMARY KEY, name TEXT NOT NULL, active NUMERIC)

objects.name: multilingualnames
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE multilingualnames (entity_id TEXT NOT NULL, language TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES languages (id), value TEXT NOT NULL, type TEXT NOT NULL, id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL UNIQUE)
